a.xlink:title: Read the battery voltage and current for all batteries. Should be called at 10hz.
returns true if battery monitor instance provides current info
voltage - returns battery voltage in millivolts
current_amps - returns the instantaneous current draw in amperes
consumed_mah - returns total current drawn since start-up in milliampere.hours
consumed_wh - returns total energy drawn since start-up in watt.hours
